{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-26","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao/la sam zvuk i vežbanje izgovaranja nazalnog konsonanta i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">ang</span> To je retro-nazalni konsonant koji počinjete da učite.</p>\n<p>Za razliku od prednjih nosnih konsonanti koje se formiraju sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">n</span> i vrh jezika iza gornjih zuba, zadnje nosne konsonante se formiraju sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ng</span>, što se postiže podizanjem zadnjeg dela jezika protiv mekog nepca.</p>\n<p>Da bi izgovorio <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ang</span>, počnite sa otvorenim vokalom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, zatim pustite zvuk da se nastavi do zadnje nazalne konsonante <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ng</span>. Držite usta otvorena i pustite zvuk da rezonuje iza grla. Ova promena ne bi smela imati prekid.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ang</span> kada je praćeno početnim konsonantima, dobija slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">bang</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">pang</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mang</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fang</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">dang</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">chang</span>.</p>\n<p>Hajde da vežbamo izgovor <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ang</span> sa tim slogovima, zatim koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fang</span> u različitim tvojima kao primeru.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fāng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">方</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fáng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">房</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fǎng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">仿</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fàng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">放</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-26"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"cafe.png","characters":[{"character":"Li Hong","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_nasal_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":377.27,"finishTimestamp":400.67},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.87,"dialogue":{"text":"ang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":3.37,"finishTime":4.09,"dialogue":{"text":"bang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.71,"finishTime":6.58,"dialogue":{"text":"pang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.86,"finishTime":8.84,"dialogue":{"text":"fang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":10.32,"finishTime":11.24,"dialogue":{"text":"dang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":12.52,"finishTime":13.49,"dialogue":{"text":"huang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":14.77,"finishTime":15.8,"dialogue":{"text":"chuang","align":"center"}},{"backgr